## **ğŸ¨ CSS (App.css)**
```css
/* Dark Mode */
.dark-mode {
  background: #121212;
  color: #f5f5f5;
}

.dark-mode .project-card {
  background: #1e1e1e;
}

/* Profile Image */
.profile-img {
  width: 150px;
  height: 150px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: 5px solid #2c3e50;
}

/* Project Grid */
.project-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 25px;
}

.project-card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}
```

---

## **ğŸ“¤ Deploy to Netlify/Vercel**
1. Push to GitHub:
   ```bash
   git add .
   git commit -m "Portfolio ready for deployment"
   git push origin main
   ```

2. **Netlify:**
   - Go to [Netlify](https://app.netlify.com)
   - Drag & drop your repo
   - Site will be live at `samuel-asante.netlify.app`

3. **Vercel:**
   ```bash
   npm install -g vercel
   vercel
   ```

---

## **ğŸ”’ Security Enhancements**
1. **FormSubmit Encryption** (free tier)
2. **CSP Headers** (in `public/index.html`)
3. **HTTPS Enforcement** (automatic on Netlify/Vercel)
4. **React Security Best Practices** (XSS protection built-in)

